WEBVTT

01:53.050 --> 01:57.520
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.500 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 28]

03:54.910 --> 03:56.040
You really are here.

03:56.350 --> 03:58.410
They all said they couldn't find you,

03:59.030 --> 04:00.310
but I still found you.

04:02.870 --> 04:04.190
How did you know I was here?

04:04.190 --> 04:04.870
I...

04:07.280 --> 04:08.150
I guessed.

04:08.680 --> 04:09.430
Don't worry.

04:09.870 --> 04:11.230
I just heard

04:11.510 --> 04:13.170
you haven't been eating much.

04:13.800 --> 04:15.130
I brought you some food.

04:16.510 --> 04:18.310
I'll leave as soon as you finish.

04:19.529 --> 04:20.589
I have no appetite.

04:24.690 --> 04:25.950
Still being stubborn.

04:28.870 --> 04:30.360
No matter what happens,

04:31.460 --> 04:33.460
eating is the most important thing.

04:33.560 --> 04:35.560
What if you starve yourself?

04:38.190 --> 04:39.360
Just eat a little.

04:40.120 --> 04:41.850
Why is it pork trotter noodles?

04:42.800 --> 04:43.600
Yeah.

04:44.070 --> 04:44.920
I...

04:45.400 --> 04:46.860
made it specially for you.

05:07.450 --> 05:08.280
How is it?

05:08.950 --> 05:10.950
After having a few bites of noodles,

05:11.600 --> 05:12.860
do you feel any better?

05:14.040 --> 05:15.630
I don't feel bad at all.

05:16.710 --> 05:19.170
I just quelled a rebellion
in the residence.

05:20.280 --> 05:22.160
This is a time to rejoice.

05:23.390 --> 05:24.500
Although

05:26.560 --> 05:29.040
I understand the principle
that a teacher for a day

05:29.040 --> 05:30.360
is a mentor for life

05:31.240 --> 05:32.360
and also know

05:32.390 --> 05:33.580
Lord Zheng once

05:33.909 --> 05:36.040
dedicated his life to the Nine Cities,

05:36.310 --> 05:37.480
for so long,

05:38.040 --> 05:39.720
he had opposed you at every turn

05:39.720 --> 05:42.000
and constantly made things
difficult for you.

05:42.000 --> 05:43.800
So, I might not be able

05:44.390 --> 05:45.720
to fully empathize with

05:45.950 --> 05:47.870
how you are feeling right now.

05:48.830 --> 05:49.720
Fan Yun.

05:52.310 --> 05:54.310
Is the path to becoming the governor

05:54.890 --> 05:56.810
always so lonely and bumpy?

05:58.890 --> 05:59.890
However,

06:01.240 --> 06:02.990
whether as your opponent

06:04.360 --> 06:05.840
or as your teacher,

06:06.950 --> 06:08.070
Lord Zheng

06:09.630 --> 06:11.160
was a man worthy of respect.

06:13.480 --> 06:14.350
You said

06:15.310 --> 06:17.040
when your second brother left,

06:17.720 --> 06:18.880
it left a wound

06:19.310 --> 06:21.160
in your heart.

06:23.040 --> 06:24.480
I think right now,

06:25.480 --> 06:27.160
you must feel the same way.

06:30.160 --> 06:31.420
But, Your Excellency,

06:32.310 --> 06:33.870
I still want to tell you

06:34.950 --> 06:35.990
what's in the past

06:37.630 --> 06:39.140
will eventually pass.

06:43.670 --> 06:45.020
Cry

06:46.550 --> 06:47.380
if you want to.

06:48.990 --> 06:50.670
Have a good cry.

06:51.340 --> 06:52.700
Because coming up next,

06:52.700 --> 06:54.550
there are more important things

06:54.550 --> 06:55.950
waiting for you to do.

07:08.460 --> 07:09.580
I won't look.

07:10.020 --> 07:11.550
Cry if you want to.

07:12.630 --> 07:14.460
I will be right here behind you.

07:32.430 --> 07:34.159
These noodles are really good.

07:37.870 --> 07:40.159
[Duanyun Gate]

07:38.990 --> 07:39.930
So,

07:40.310 --> 07:42.510
how did you notice something was wrong?

07:43.580 --> 07:45.580
It was the eunuch who brought me out.

07:45.750 --> 07:46.260
At first,

07:46.260 --> 07:48.110
I just thought he looked unfamiliar.

07:48.110 --> 07:49.190
Then,

07:49.190 --> 07:51.520
I noticed his sleeves
were a bit too short.

07:51.820 --> 07:53.950
Those obviously weren't his clothes.

07:59.310 --> 08:00.190
Anyway,

08:02.580 --> 08:03.510
thank you.

08:05.100 --> 08:05.750
By the way,

08:06.340 --> 08:07.310
do you think

08:08.460 --> 08:10.720
we should tell Second Young Master Zheng

08:11.190 --> 08:12.990
the news of Elder Zheng's death?

08:16.550 --> 08:18.820
Zheng Yuan's rebellion happened suddenly.

08:18.820 --> 08:20.580
It hasn't been fully investigated yet.

08:20.580 --> 08:22.580
It's not a good time to visit him now.

08:27.580 --> 08:28.730
But Zheng Shi...

08:28.780 --> 08:29.950
You want to say

08:30.380 --> 08:32.380
Zheng Shi is not that kind of person?

08:34.789 --> 08:36.190
But what you need to do now

08:36.500 --> 08:38.159
is go back and get a good sleep.

08:38.620 --> 08:40.950
We can talk about everything else
after you wake up.

08:40.950 --> 08:43.280
The carriage is already prepared for you.

08:48.500 --> 08:49.220
Thank you.

08:52.220 --> 08:53.040
Hurry back.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.070
Okay.

08:54.740 --> 08:56.600
Then you should get some rest too.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.430
Gao Ran.

09:12.740 --> 09:13.950
Did you

09:14.620 --> 09:15.950
already know about it?

09:17.150 --> 09:19.080
Just a little earlier than you did.

09:19.270 --> 09:20.760
When His Excellency told me

09:20.760 --> 09:22.740
that Lord Fan Qi was in the Dark Wolves,

09:22.740 --> 09:24.200
I was also very surprised.

09:25.620 --> 09:26.340
Really?

09:29.550 --> 09:30.820
I just didn't expect

09:31.190 --> 09:31.820
that Dad

09:32.340 --> 09:34.540
would have such incredible abilities.

09:35.220 --> 09:36.790
A true master hides in plain sight.

09:36.790 --> 09:38.920
We underestimated Lord Fan Qi before.

09:40.220 --> 09:41.760
I used to think

09:41.950 --> 09:44.310
Dad was unathletic and ignorant.

09:44.820 --> 09:46.680
Turns out I was completely wrong.

09:47.500 --> 09:48.310
However,

09:49.190 --> 09:51.120
I still don't understand why Dad

09:51.500 --> 09:52.880
kept it a secret from us.

09:54.460 --> 09:56.100
Because he is a secret guard
of the Qi family,

09:56.100 --> 09:56.950
he naturally couldn't reveal his identity

09:56.950 --> 09:58.080
casually to others.

09:58.620 --> 10:00.340
Especially to those close to him.

10:00.340 --> 10:01.670
The less we know,

10:01.910 --> 10:02.840
the safer we are.

10:03.700 --> 10:04.500
Lord Fan Qi

10:04.740 --> 10:05.910
has always been using this method

10:05.910 --> 10:06.950
to protect us.

10:09.430 --> 10:10.070
It seems Dad

10:10.070 --> 10:12.530
also have many difficulties and hardships.

10:12.910 --> 10:13.700
From now on,

10:14.070 --> 10:15.870
we should treat him even better.

10:23.030 --> 10:24.110
-Again.
-Again.

10:30.220 --> 10:31.990
Your Excellency, I implore you

10:33.070 --> 10:36.220
to leave Zheng Yuan's body intact!

10:36.740 --> 10:38.470
Your Excellency, I implore you

10:39.790 --> 10:41.030
to let me

10:42.070 --> 10:44.500
take away Zheng Yuan's body.

10:45.580 --> 10:47.430
Your Excellency, I implore you

10:48.580 --> 10:52.190
to leave Zheng Yuan's body intact.

10:56.870 --> 10:58.080
Your Excellency, as long as you

10:58.080 --> 11:00.590
agree to my request,

11:02.430 --> 11:03.920
I am willing

11:04.550 --> 11:06.480
to resign and return to my hometown

11:06.860 --> 11:08.370
to calm the people's

11:08.550 --> 11:10.070
dissatisfaction.

11:11.460 --> 11:13.060
I also request

11:13.230 --> 11:14.710
to retire.

11:15.670 --> 11:17.030
Lord Lyu, Lord Zhao,

11:17.820 --> 11:18.460
is this

11:18.460 --> 11:20.520
what trusted ministers should say?

11:27.630 --> 11:29.150
Please, Your Excellency,

11:30.190 --> 11:35.100
preserve the body of Lord Zheng Yuan.

11:38.740 --> 11:40.470
I respect you both as my elders,

11:40.700 --> 11:43.310
but you shouldn't take advantage
of my youth to bully me.

11:43.310 --> 11:45.530
Zheng Yuan's crime of treason is a fact.

11:46.360 --> 11:47.620
You can't plead for him

11:47.620 --> 11:49.550
just because you are good friends.

11:49.700 --> 11:50.270
Besides,

11:51.430 --> 11:54.490
it was Lord Lyu who taught me
that the law shows no mercy.

11:57.860 --> 11:59.100
Your Excellency,

11:59.950 --> 12:01.520
how would we

12:01.950 --> 12:03.990
dare to look down on you?

12:05.150 --> 12:07.860
Your Excellency, think about it.

12:08.430 --> 12:10.860
Zheng had a large army

12:11.820 --> 12:13.310
in Jing City.

12:13.820 --> 12:15.670
If he had intended to rebel,

12:15.980 --> 12:20.490
how could he have trespassed
into the Qi Residence with just a few men,

12:21.100 --> 12:23.460
been easily captured,

12:23.460 --> 12:26.190
-and lost his life?
-Zhao.

12:27.190 --> 12:28.820
Your Excellency.

12:30.580 --> 12:31.860
Your Excellency.

12:32.170 --> 12:33.110
Zhao.

12:34.400 --> 12:35.970
Stop talking.

12:37.500 --> 12:39.660
He injured the official
administering the selection exam

12:39.660 --> 12:40.990
and almost killed me.

12:42.490 --> 12:44.250
No matter the reason,

12:45.310 --> 12:46.550
it is treason.

12:47.620 --> 12:49.220
I beg you, Your Excellency,

12:50.700 --> 12:52.550
to see clearly.

13:01.050 --> 13:04.130
Elder Zheng was an important minister
for 3 generations

13:04.130 --> 13:06.220
and an elder of the Nine Cities.

13:07.700 --> 13:10.960
Considering he dedicated
half his life to the Nine Cities,

13:11.030 --> 13:13.960
I grant a special pardon
and order him to be cremated.

13:18.550 --> 13:20.880
His family is pardoned from implication.

13:25.740 --> 13:29.740
-Thank you, Your Excellency.
-Thank you, Your Excellency!

13:59.220 --> 13:59.950
Tell me,

14:00.410 --> 14:01.950
how can a perfectly fine person,

14:01.950 --> 14:03.870
in the blink of an eye,

14:04.530 --> 14:06.340
just be cremated

14:06.370 --> 14:08.530
and turn into ashes?

14:11.110 --> 14:11.900
People

14:14.460 --> 14:15.680
will always

14:16.070 --> 14:17.730
return to the earth in the end.

14:22.460 --> 14:24.030
This Zheng...

14:24.910 --> 14:26.790
Why were you so stubborn?

14:27.390 --> 14:29.740
How could you do such a thing?

14:29.740 --> 14:31.400
How could you commit treason?

14:32.670 --> 14:34.390
You were sharp all your life,

14:34.390 --> 14:36.070
yet stumbled this once.

14:36.340 --> 14:37.220
Let it go.

14:39.100 --> 14:40.270
Zheng

14:41.430 --> 14:43.490
was definitely not a foolish person.

14:45.620 --> 14:47.620
He followed the late governor

14:47.620 --> 14:49.950
and fought everywhere in his early years.

14:50.790 --> 14:52.770
He was already

14:52.910 --> 14:56.220
riddled with hidden injuries
and physically drained.

14:58.960 --> 15:01.280
Even if his body was failing,

15:01.820 --> 15:03.390
he wouldn't resort to this

15:05.270 --> 15:07.860
for a final struggle.

15:10.190 --> 15:11.430
Furthermore,

15:12.550 --> 15:13.750
since His Excellency

15:14.740 --> 15:16.270
took over the administration,

15:16.270 --> 15:18.270
he has been doing better and better.

15:18.910 --> 15:20.980
And he has also seen

15:21.790 --> 15:24.590
the efforts of the young people
in the Nine Cities.

15:31.700 --> 15:33.460
I can't speak as you do.

15:33.980 --> 15:36.240
I only know Zheng was smarter than me.

15:36.550 --> 15:37.830
And you are too.

16:29.700 --> 16:31.190
My grandson, Shi,

16:32.440 --> 16:34.020
you started speaking at 3,

16:35.550 --> 16:37.070
reciting poetry at 5,

16:38.150 --> 16:39.650
and practicing sword at 7.

16:41.340 --> 16:43.280
Your only flaw is being tone-deaf,

16:44.430 --> 16:47.220
with nothing else to criticize.

16:49.700 --> 16:51.700
I have spent my life in the military,

16:53.500 --> 16:56.450
conquering the world for the Nine Cities.

16:57.030 --> 17:00.260
I experienced war and struggles
for succession,

17:00.740 --> 17:04.200
yet always bearing
too many responsibilities.

17:12.589 --> 17:13.500
Therefore,

17:14.740 --> 17:16.020
I always thought

17:17.109 --> 17:19.950
that you were capable of inheriting

17:20.500 --> 17:24.119
the great responsibility
of the Zheng family as my grandson.

17:25.500 --> 17:27.099
But I forgot

17:28.870 --> 17:32.380
that you have your own life.

17:34.590 --> 17:36.020
My grandson, Shi,

17:37.200 --> 17:38.880
just go and live

17:39.370 --> 17:43.680
the free life you want.

17:45.540 --> 17:47.340
As for those responsibilities,

17:47.590 --> 17:49.700
let me alone

17:50.970 --> 17:52.810
shoulder them.

17:55.740 --> 17:57.930
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

17:58.030 --> 18:01.990
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

18:02.100 --> 18:04.590
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

18:04.610 --> 18:08.970
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

18:07.260 --> 18:09.190
I'm sorry, Shi.

18:08.990 --> 18:11.630
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

18:11.220 --> 18:13.590
If your back still hurts,

18:11.650 --> 18:16.500
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

18:14.910 --> 18:18.430
it means I miss you.

18:16.510 --> 18:23.200
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

18:23.740 --> 18:35.220
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

18:49.170 --> 18:50.700
Second Young Master Zheng.

18:55.700 --> 18:56.630
Where are you

18:57.060 --> 18:58.060
right now?

18:59.630 --> 19:01.160
Second Young Master Zheng.

19:03.050 --> 19:04.360
Are you alright?

19:07.890 --> 19:10.470
[All Worthies Gather Here]

19:26.430 --> 19:28.040
Young Master Shi, it's late.

19:28.070 --> 19:29.070
We should set off.

19:49.190 --> 19:50.190
Young Master Shi!

19:51.350 --> 19:52.460
Please calm down.

19:53.350 --> 19:54.670
Don't force my hand.

19:55.060 --> 19:56.660
Tell me everything you know.

19:57.500 --> 19:58.670
Master only ordered

19:58.670 --> 20:00.600
to send you as far away as possible.

20:07.100 --> 20:08.960
Grandfather is no longer with us.

20:11.060 --> 20:13.460
From now on, I am in charge
of the Zheng family.

20:13.460 --> 20:14.700
Set off back to Ling'an.

20:14.700 --> 20:15.700
Young Master Shi,

20:16.220 --> 20:17.880
you read Master's letter too.

20:17.950 --> 20:19.590
By sending you away at this time,

20:19.590 --> 20:20.260
he hoped you

20:20.260 --> 20:22.120
can stay away from Ling'an
and the Zheng family from now on,

20:22.120 --> 20:23.800
living a quiet life.

20:23.870 --> 20:25.800
Why must you go against his wishes?

20:30.290 --> 20:32.050
I must accomplish

20:32.650 --> 20:34.020
what I decide to do.

20:35.890 --> 20:38.950
[Taiji Palace]

20:39.670 --> 20:41.010
Zheng Yuan's treason

20:41.220 --> 20:42.480
happened so suddenly.

20:43.390 --> 20:45.220
Everyone is shocked and confused.

20:45.220 --> 20:47.950
Many commoners and officials
are involved in it.

20:48.060 --> 20:48.710
Today,

20:48.950 --> 20:50.950
in front of all my beloved ministers,

20:50.950 --> 20:52.950
I will personally interrogate Zheng Yi

20:52.950 --> 20:54.880
and give everyone an explanation.

20:55.150 --> 20:58.040
Summon the criminal Zheng Yi to the hall.

21:08.220 --> 21:08.980
Untie him.

21:09.430 --> 21:11.150
Let him step forward and answer.

21:11.150 --> 21:12.150
Your Excellency.

21:13.110 --> 21:14.390
This is inappropriate, isn't it?

21:14.390 --> 21:16.650
When the heart fades, the lamp dies away.

21:16.760 --> 21:18.350
I have my own considerations.

21:18.350 --> 21:19.120
Untie him.

21:23.670 --> 21:24.390
Zheng Yi.

21:25.020 --> 21:27.020
I have already sent Zheng Yuan's ashes

21:27.020 --> 21:28.620
back to the Zheng Residence.

21:30.460 --> 21:32.060
Sent back to the Zheng Residence?

21:32.060 --> 21:34.190
It was because these two lords
risked their lives to plead for him,

21:34.190 --> 21:36.220
so I canceled
the public exposure of the corpse

21:36.220 --> 21:38.020
and replaced it with cremation.

21:38.040 --> 21:39.540
Thank you, Your Excellency.

21:39.540 --> 21:40.550
Get up first.

21:41.460 --> 21:43.520
I have a few questions to ask clearly.

21:46.380 --> 21:48.380
Why hasn't Zheng Shi shown up yet?

21:49.110 --> 21:50.880
Before the incident,

21:51.220 --> 21:53.840
Young Master Shi was forcibly
escorted away by Master.

21:53.840 --> 21:56.320
He knows nothing about this matter.

21:56.700 --> 21:57.390
Good.

21:58.590 --> 22:00.910
You really cleared
Zheng Shi's name completely.

22:00.910 --> 22:01.870
Your Excellency,

22:01.870 --> 22:03.910
you know Young Master Shi's temperament.

22:03.910 --> 22:05.740
If he had known about this matter,

22:05.740 --> 22:07.070
he surely wouldn't have

22:07.190 --> 22:08.550
just hidden away.

22:09.190 --> 22:11.650
Master and Young Master Shi
have a deep bond.

22:11.950 --> 22:13.220
Regarding this matter,

22:13.220 --> 22:16.020
he wouldn't let Young Master Shi
be involved in it.

22:16.570 --> 22:19.230
Please investigate clearly,
Your Excellency.

22:19.390 --> 22:20.720
Regarding the treason,

22:21.590 --> 22:23.120
besides you and Zheng Yuan,

22:23.980 --> 22:25.240
who else knew about it?

22:25.670 --> 22:26.350
Treason

22:27.390 --> 22:29.050
was just my and Master's idea.

22:29.350 --> 22:31.350
This matter is of great importance!

22:31.740 --> 22:33.600
Think clearly before answering!

22:34.240 --> 22:37.220
Only dozens of Zheng's Army soldiers
entered the residence that night,

22:37.220 --> 22:39.350
and they were all stationed
in Ling'an year-round

22:39.350 --> 22:40.950
to protect the Zheng family.

22:41.240 --> 22:44.100
Not a single soldier
was dispatched from Jing City.

22:44.220 --> 22:45.220
I know

22:45.500 --> 22:47.360
I have no right to plead for mercy.

22:47.430 --> 22:48.540
But Your Excellency,

22:48.540 --> 22:51.270
if you still have a trace of affection
for Master,

22:51.320 --> 22:52.440
you should know

22:53.040 --> 22:55.700
that he was definitely
not the kind of person...

22:56.520 --> 22:58.850
who would commit treason and usurp power.

23:00.950 --> 23:02.330
Your Excellency!

23:04.290 --> 23:06.100
-Elder Zheng.
-Your Excellency.

23:06.100 --> 23:09.260
Since the implementation
of the national selection exam,

23:09.260 --> 23:10.990
the nobles have been restless.

23:12.700 --> 23:14.260
They have obstructed it several times,

23:14.260 --> 23:15.660
shaking the foundation.

23:16.570 --> 23:17.300
Among them,

23:17.540 --> 23:19.250
the Zheng family in Jing City

23:19.900 --> 23:21.820
has made the most frequent moves,

23:22.390 --> 23:23.450
even hiring people

23:25.260 --> 23:28.780
to snatch the sweet wormwood
and ruin the selection exam.

23:34.390 --> 23:35.870
Then why are you
putting on this show of treason,

23:35.870 --> 23:36.740
Elder Zheng?

23:37.980 --> 23:40.840
There's an undercurrent
in the current situation.

23:40.870 --> 23:42.400
I'm afraid the Zheng family

23:42.760 --> 23:44.950
already has the intention of treason.

23:49.150 --> 23:51.110
The Zheng family in Jing City

23:51.110 --> 23:52.650
has a strong military.

23:52.950 --> 23:54.190
Once they rebel,

23:54.740 --> 23:56.350
there will be countless casualties,

23:56.350 --> 23:57.950
and the people will suffer.

24:00.260 --> 24:01.120
So,

24:01.730 --> 24:05.170
I struck first today

24:05.260 --> 24:08.430
just to remind you, Your Excellency.

24:14.740 --> 24:15.510
Although

24:16.630 --> 24:18.730
the chance of success is slim,

24:19.220 --> 24:20.460
the Nine Cities'

24:20.460 --> 24:22.520
strong leadership and mighty forces

24:22.830 --> 24:24.500
are clear to all,

24:24.500 --> 24:26.570
enough to deter Jing City.

24:29.780 --> 24:31.580
I only beg you, Your Excellency,

24:31.910 --> 24:33.220
to pardon

24:33.700 --> 24:39.300
the innocent descendants
of the Zheng family in Jing City.

24:40.510 --> 24:42.710
So you acted before the Zheng family

24:43.700 --> 24:45.360
to save the people of Jing City

24:46.220 --> 24:47.550
from the disaster of war

24:48.060 --> 24:49.590
and to disrupt their plans?

24:49.780 --> 24:50.790
Exactly.

24:57.850 --> 24:58.770
Elder Zheng,

24:59.980 --> 25:01.440
why did you have to do this?

25:01.540 --> 25:03.500
We could have taken
our time to discuss this.

25:03.500 --> 25:05.150
It's too late!

25:11.830 --> 25:12.830
One step earlier,

25:13.590 --> 25:15.190
and you gain the upper hand.

25:15.700 --> 25:16.810
One step later,

25:17.390 --> 25:18.910
and you lose everything.

25:20.540 --> 25:22.260
You.

25:23.950 --> 25:25.060
You forgot again.

25:26.590 --> 25:27.770
Have you forgotten

25:28.350 --> 25:29.350
what I taught you

25:29.630 --> 25:32.100
when you were a child?

25:44.020 --> 25:45.010
I am old.

25:47.110 --> 25:48.460
I am now

25:48.980 --> 25:50.640
a candle in the wind,

25:51.350 --> 25:52.980
flickering.

25:55.630 --> 25:57.830
I hope this remaining glimmer of light

25:58.950 --> 26:00.430
can illuminate

26:01.910 --> 26:03.060
your path

26:03.630 --> 26:06.110
ahead, Your Excellency.

26:08.700 --> 26:09.830
Then I

26:11.190 --> 26:12.720
die with no regrets.

26:16.020 --> 26:17.430
I don't agree.

26:20.110 --> 26:21.060
I can agree to anything

26:21.060 --> 26:22.110
you say, Elder Zheng,

26:22.110 --> 26:23.260
But I will never

26:25.870 --> 26:27.060
agree to this.

26:30.190 --> 26:33.360
Then I will teach you one more time!

26:39.390 --> 26:40.150
Elder Zheng!

26:55.740 --> 26:57.270
-Your Excellency!
-Zheng!

26:57.660 --> 26:59.070
-Zheng!
-Zheng!

27:05.310 --> 27:06.270
Elder Zheng!

27:06.300 --> 27:07.300
Your Excellency!

27:07.600 --> 27:08.450
This is...

27:08.770 --> 27:09.660
Zheng!

27:16.780 --> 27:18.040
Since that is the case,

27:19.020 --> 27:20.620
regarding the Zheng family,

27:21.580 --> 27:24.580
I will absolutely not implicate
any innocent people,

27:25.100 --> 27:27.780
nor will I let any bad apples go.

27:28.170 --> 27:29.770
Thank you, Your Excellency.

27:30.390 --> 27:32.120
You are wise, Your Excellency!

27:32.350 --> 27:35.950
-You are wise, Your Excellency!
-You are wise, Your Excellency!

27:43.950 --> 27:46.260
His Excellency is generous and merciful,

27:46.260 --> 27:48.260
sparing you from the death penalty.

27:48.830 --> 27:50.690
I can only repay His Excellency's

27:51.390 --> 27:53.300
great kindness in my next life.

27:54.150 --> 27:55.300
In this life,

27:55.910 --> 27:57.260
I will follow Master.

27:59.780 --> 28:00.740
I, Zheng Yi,

28:01.150 --> 28:02.880
having met Master in this life,

28:03.550 --> 28:05.220
have found my roots.

28:06.460 --> 28:07.700
I hope His Excellency

28:09.020 --> 28:12.020
can understand Master's
lonely and resolute heart.

28:13.230 --> 28:15.230
Master is already on the other side.

28:15.370 --> 28:16.970
I can't let him wait too long.

28:52.390 --> 28:53.430
Your Excellency?

29:01.740 --> 29:02.740
Your Excellency.

29:04.780 --> 29:05.850
Why didn't you let me know

29:05.850 --> 29:07.290
you were coming here?

29:08.770 --> 29:10.490
Lord Fan Qi brought me in.

29:12.950 --> 29:13.680
You went out?

29:14.540 --> 29:15.110
Yes.

29:15.300 --> 29:17.020
I went out to buy some ingredients.

29:17.020 --> 29:17.950
I'm going

29:17.950 --> 29:19.910
to make some buns
for Dad and Gao Ran tonight.

29:19.910 --> 29:21.050
You should stay too.

29:22.740 --> 29:24.110
I won't stay to eat.

29:24.830 --> 29:27.360
I just wanted to see you,
and then I'll go back.

29:28.540 --> 29:30.430
What's wrong?

29:31.060 --> 29:32.250
You look so down.

29:33.740 --> 29:34.590
I'm fine.

29:35.950 --> 29:36.430
No.

29:37.870 --> 29:39.270
If it had been in the past,

29:39.500 --> 29:41.160
you would have been thrilled.

29:41.220 --> 29:41.980
You would have insisted on staying

29:41.980 --> 29:43.460
to eat buns with us.

29:43.830 --> 29:45.490
Why aren't you staying today?

29:51.260 --> 29:52.220
Two buns

29:52.730 --> 29:54.010
for the truth.

29:54.210 --> 29:55.620
What exactly happened?

29:58.190 --> 30:00.190
Three, and they're meat buns.

30:00.690 --> 30:01.620
Zheng Yi is dead.

30:07.910 --> 30:08.620
Sorry.

30:09.740 --> 30:10.740
I should get back.

30:12.260 --> 30:12.870
Qi Zheng.

30:17.910 --> 30:19.280
I told him that day

30:20.020 --> 30:21.610
that everyone dies eventually,

30:21.610 --> 30:24.980
and that the only thing that matters
is dying for a worthy cause.

30:24.980 --> 30:26.100
Now it seems

30:27.170 --> 30:28.380
he thought so too.

30:30.340 --> 30:31.520
So you really

30:32.340 --> 30:34.470
don't need to blame yourself too much.

30:37.260 --> 30:38.430
Actually,

30:38.430 --> 30:40.760
whether it's Zheng Yuan or Zheng Yi,

30:41.700 --> 30:43.130
they are the same as us.

30:44.060 --> 30:46.720
They were all doing
what they truly believed in.

30:48.220 --> 30:49.740
Winning or losing,

30:50.350 --> 30:51.390
they were prepared for

30:51.390 --> 30:52.350
the worst

30:53.190 --> 30:54.520
and willingly accepted

30:54.540 --> 30:55.720
any outcome.

30:57.830 --> 30:58.760
Don't you think?

31:09.700 --> 31:11.960
What are you going to treat me to tonight?

31:14.980 --> 31:16.510
Delicious buns, of course.

31:16.870 --> 31:18.090
But you have to stay

31:18.260 --> 31:19.460
and make them with me.

31:24.830 --> 31:25.630
Grandfather.

31:34.980 --> 31:35.780
Grandfather.

31:36.010 --> 31:38.160
A document has been sent from Ling'an.

31:39.740 --> 31:40.560
Read it.

31:44.350 --> 31:45.750
By order of the Governor,

31:45.810 --> 31:48.020
Master Zheng Yuan
led troops into the residence,

31:48.020 --> 31:50.060
committed insubordination,
coerced the Governor,

31:50.060 --> 31:53.060
and harmed colleagues.
His crimes are unpardonable.

31:53.390 --> 31:55.250
He has now committed suicide
to escape punishment.

31:55.250 --> 31:57.540
Zheng Yuan is stripped of
his honorable title

31:57.540 --> 31:59.430
and shall be cremated.

31:59.630 --> 32:00.670
However, upon investigation,

32:00.670 --> 32:01.910
the rest of the Zheng family

32:01.910 --> 32:03.830
has no connection to the rebellion.

32:03.830 --> 32:05.910
Therefore, no further action
will be taken.

32:05.910 --> 32:07.830
Zheng Tao is specially
permitted to enter Ling'an

32:07.830 --> 32:10.360
to bring Zheng Yuan's ashes
back to Jing City,

32:10.390 --> 32:11.990
so he may return to his roots.

32:13.840 --> 32:14.470
So

32:15.300 --> 32:17.640
the rebellion
is just brushed off like this?

32:17.640 --> 32:19.240
It seems the rumors are true.

32:19.980 --> 32:21.740
Qi Zheng is indeed a loser.

32:22.290 --> 32:23.390
I'm afraid

32:24.980 --> 32:26.350
it's a stalling tactic.

32:27.390 --> 32:30.250
Eldest Brother's treason
was already a huge taboo.

32:30.290 --> 32:33.020
Not only did His Excellency
not punish Jing City,

32:33.190 --> 32:35.970
but he also cremated him
and returned his ashes.

32:37.700 --> 32:39.630
This is a favor to Jing City.

32:41.060 --> 32:42.740
Showing favor instead of punishing

32:42.740 --> 32:44.070
is indeed a bit strange.

32:44.740 --> 32:46.140
Grandfather, do you mean

32:46.830 --> 32:47.890
that this is a trap?

32:49.040 --> 32:49.880
Grandfather.

32:50.540 --> 32:52.800
Why don't we find an excuse

32:53.190 --> 32:54.290
and just not go?

32:55.060 --> 32:56.720
It is His Excellency's order.

32:56.910 --> 32:58.500
I have no reason not to go.

32:59.950 --> 33:01.410
My eldest brother's ashes

33:02.260 --> 33:04.390
must also be brought back to Jing City.

33:06.260 --> 33:07.440
If I don't go,

33:07.670 --> 33:09.570
not only will I fail
to account for this to Jing City,

33:09.570 --> 33:12.370
but the other cities
will also make a joke out of us.

33:13.670 --> 33:14.550
I must go

33:16.740 --> 33:17.950
this time.

33:21.020 --> 33:22.190
By the way, Grandfather,

33:22.190 --> 33:23.460
the Gate Commander Residence

33:23.460 --> 33:25.540
also received His Excellency's order,

33:25.540 --> 33:27.120
saying Liu Mu should go...

33:27.540 --> 33:29.270
to take up his post in Ling'an.

33:29.830 --> 33:30.550
Now,

33:30.980 --> 33:32.980
I'm afraid we can't hide it anymore.

33:33.270 --> 33:34.200
That's perfect.

33:36.110 --> 33:37.710
Let the news of Liu Mu's death

33:37.830 --> 33:40.820
stir up the recently calmed Ling'an again.

33:41.110 --> 33:42.840
Our Jing City has a strong army.

33:42.950 --> 33:44.810
We don't fear schemes and tricks.

33:44.980 --> 33:47.630
As the saying goes,
absolute power overcomes all tricks.

33:47.630 --> 33:50.030
At worst, we'll fight him
to the bitter end.

33:53.630 --> 33:54.850
You're right.

34:02.190 --> 34:04.390
This might be an opportunity.

34:03.680 --> 34:06.670
[Zheng Tao,
Second Master of the Zheng family]

34:06.300 --> 34:07.590
So for this trip,

34:08.350 --> 34:09.560
not only must I go,

34:10.159 --> 34:12.090
but I must also beat gongs and drums

34:12.100 --> 34:13.650
and go with great fanfare.

34:17.100 --> 34:19.170
I will accept the favor

34:20.510 --> 34:21.770
from that boy Qi Zheng.

34:23.580 --> 34:25.980
The position of Jing City's gate commander

34:26.270 --> 34:28.800
must absolutely
not fall into others' hands.

34:30.830 --> 34:31.690
This time,

34:34.010 --> 34:34.810
Xian,

34:35.460 --> 34:37.320
you will accompany me to Ling'an.

34:38.000 --> 34:40.150
Jin, you will guard Jing City.

34:40.540 --> 34:41.139
Yes.

34:43.860 --> 34:45.710
But with Zheng Yuan passing away,

34:45.710 --> 34:48.100
the position of the Zheng family's master
falls vacant.

34:48.100 --> 34:50.300
This Jing City must not fall into chaos.

34:51.310 --> 34:54.310
Succession to the position
across the Nine Noble Families

34:54.310 --> 34:56.840
has always fallen
to the younger generation.

34:57.900 --> 34:59.830
Now that my eldest brother is dead,

35:00.020 --> 35:02.420
it can only fall to your generation.

35:04.790 --> 35:05.790
A storm is coming.

35:06.160 --> 35:07.690
It's a good time for me to see

35:08.180 --> 35:10.560
who is truly capable of bearing
the responsibility of the Zheng family.
